    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras/57a5eb3dd898a8a8831f4669d72e78f6.avif?t=1762357165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras_big/57a5eb3dd898a8a8831f4669d72e78f6.webp?t=1762357165 width=1560 height=878 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a vampire cat trying to run a barbershop… without biting the costumers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wash, cut, shave chat and fight your thirst. One haircut at a time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras/0d63f488797c532b6a2631ba63357c01.avif?t=1762357165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras_big/0d63f488797c532b6a2631ba63357c01.webp?t=1762357165 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cut hair and trim beards with precision and quick reflexes. As your bloodlust increases, your controls get reversed.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wash hair while dealing with a few tricky inverted arrows.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each task gets harder the thirstier you become. And you thought pretty doesn’t hurt.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras/d9149bddb13db1c11e0b0756454d1626.avif?t=1762357165\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746710/extras_big/d9149bddb13db1c11e0b0756454d1626.webp?t=1762357165 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bad cuts or bloody accidents will hurt your reputation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your performance influences the story, unlocking different endings. Some hilarious, others unsettling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Messed up? Clean up the evidence quickly or risk raising suspicion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ignore a single stain, and it might cost your credibility (or your costumer).</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Characteristics</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique bloodlust mechanic that affects the game’s difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings based on your performance</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minigames that get harder each day</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An eccentric and atmospheric soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Characters full of dark humor</p></li></ul>",
